data.description: Welcome Home to this Beautiful Bi-Level home in Popular Pebble Creek by Edwin Allen Homes! The first level includes a Large Primary Bedroom with hardwood flooring, a Huge walk in closet & attached bath that includes Custom vanity lighting, shower door, & touch-less flush, as well a 2nd, ample size, bedroom. An Open Great room & Kitchen area boasts vaulted ceilings, hardwood flooring & custom ceiling fans & lighting. This Custom Kitchen area features Plenty of Custom Cabinets, for ample Storage, Custom Tile back splash, stone facing snack bar, custom pull out lower unit shelving & a pantry with extra shelving from floor to ceiling as well as stainless steel appliances, & a doorwall that takes you out to your "forever" Trex style deck, with wrought iron railing, overlooking the huge, totally fenced in, back yard, with stairs leading to lower level! The "Back" piece of the yard has Wire Fencing to preserve the view of the trees.  The Cozy lower level includes lots of daylight windows that allow for bright natural light, a large family room with sliding barn door window covers, & 2 well sized bedrooms, as well as the lower level full bathroom that also has custom vanity lighting and touchless flush. Builders Upgraded Arched raised panel doors and custom blinds and shades throughout.  The attached, 2 & half car, garage is finished & dry walled, insulated & painted, with epoxy floor finish, & a Gorgeous Carriage Style Double Door. An extra large driveway welcomes you home, with parking pad & Double gates off of the driveway that Open up to Beautiful Stone Paver Patio out back with Stairway leading up to Large Trex Style Deck, with Welcoming Doorwall to the upper level Great room! Situated in the Grand Blanc School System. "RING" is included -buyer to hookup online after closing. See it before it is GONE - ALL OFFERS WILL BE PRESENTED AS RECEIVED SO SEND YOU BEST FIRST !!
